data.description: HIDDEN GEM located at Pioneer Point in Waxahachie, Texas. Conveniently located within minutes of major intersections, shopping, dining, entertainment, award winning school district, & DOWNTOWN DALLAS. Exterior boasts of brick, 1 acre, single story, corner lot, with extended driveway, side entry 2 car garage, septic, firepit, covered porch, & patio. This 4 br, 3.5 bath, showcases, elevated ceilings, modern fixtures, & a combination of wood, ceramic tile, & plush carpet flooring. Open kitchen & family concept includes a fireplace, granite countertops, extended bartop, island, walk in pantry, breakfast nook, & garden sink. Separate laundry area & study with built in desk and shelving, & huge FLEX ROOM.  Owners Suite has cathedral ceilings, dual sinks, separate walk in shower, garden tub, & a huge walk in closet with built in shelving. Additional bedrooms are spacious & located on the opposite side of home. All major systems are in pristine condition. This is a MUST SEE!
